Ask HN: Simplest CMS for blog type website
text: Hi, my wife and I are planning a long adventure trip and I wanted to create some some sort of travel blog with Next.js or similar stack that I'm familiar with. The problem is my wife will probably write most of the content and she is not technical at all so I'm looking for a very simple CMS, easy to setup and free where she could write up stories and publish them on a daily basis. Mostly text, images and maybe videos. I've looked at some headless CMS on jamstack.org but they're so many ...

Ask HN: Your Favourite Live-Coding Streamers
text:
I've realised I'm no longer enjoying coding -- especially at work.

In addition to clearing away the causes for that, I also want to remember what makes it so fun. I'd like to watch talented people do neat things, to understand why they're making interesting choices and to share their joy in creation.
